REQURED PACKAGES
For compiling sources and general command line development, you need these
packages. All are installed via apt-get

  build-essential
  vim
  git
  libssl-dev
  libcurl4-openssl-dev
  libexpat1-dev
  libpython-dev
  libpython3-dev
  texlive-full (this takes a few hours...)
  asciidoc
  xmlto
  docbook2x
  python-wxgtk2.8
